<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154682" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2">Use a <emph>Master Document</emph> to organize complex projects, such as a book. <ahelp hid=".">A <emph>Master Document</emph> can contain the individual files for each chapter of a book, as well as a table of contents, and an index.</ahelp></paragraph>
